text: Wincrange (, ) is a commune in Luxembourg. It is part of the canton of Clervaux. It is the largest commune in Luxembourg by area. As of 2019, 4,392 people live here. Wincrange was created on 1 January 1978 from the former communes of Asselborn, Boevange, Hachiville and Oberwampach. Category:1978 establishments in Europe Category:Communes of Clervaux
